"{\"uid\": \"nbcbayarea.com-paris-2024-summer-olympics-u-s-mens-water-polo-team-plays-off-against-spain-at-cal-ahead-of-paris-3579935\", \"text\": \"Although the U.S. Olympic trials are underway, the U.S. men's water polo team is playing a game ahead of Paris.  The men played an exhibition match agaisnt Spin at the University of California, Berkeley's Speiker Aquatics Complex Friday.  Watch NBC Bay Area News free wherever you are  It's one of the teams' last at-home games before they head to Europe.  \\\"I am so happy to be back, it's awesome,\\\" said Johnny Hopper, a Cal graduate.  Hopper is just one of many on the team with Bay Area ties.  The team is set to play again on Sunday.\"}"